19 NEW SECTION. Section 3. Ambiguity in operating agreement regarding dissolution. If there is
20 an ambiguity in an operating agreement between a construction in favor of maintaining the existence of a
21 limited liability company or in favor of the dissolution of a limited liability company, the operating agreement
22 must be construed in favor of maintaining the existence of the limited liability company.
23
24 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Appropriation. There is appropriated $100 from the general fund to the
25 office of secretary of state for the fiscal year beginning July 1, 2025, for the purpose of updating the agency's
26 website to reflect the changes pursuant to [section 1].
